From 2cb45c1f65671498377a001734afa29c4f494b38 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 6 Aug 2025 10:26:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:CP Accumulate and print peer airtime stats from PPDU
 stats

Accumulate airtime for each peer and radio from PPDU stats.
Maintain separate counters for radio-level and per-peer airtime.
On stats enablement, aggregate peer airtime by group and print
the results.

Add infrastructure to dump peer and radio airtime per WMM AC to
userspace. Send accumulated stats to hostapd upon receiving NL
vendor command.

Signed-off-by: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
